platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Weve played so many games that we feel like we could create our ownand now we can, all without coding classes or complex tutorials. With this ingenious educational app, it's easy to become a designer. Imagination rules as you build characters, worlds, and stories for one-of-a-kind games meant to be saved, shared, andof courseplayed.
